9. What role does IoT play in this market? IoT facilitates wireless connectivity and remote management of audio systems, improving efficiency.

10. Are there any eco-friendly developments in the industry? Yes, manufacturers are focusing on energy-efficient and sustainable audio solutions to meet environmental goals.

